Creating the documentation
*****************************

You need the html-documentation of Qt for creating the doxytag-file so 
doxygen can create a full class hierarchy with Qt classes.
Create the file with: 
doxytag -t qt.tag /path/to/qt/doc  
e.g.: doxytag -t qt.tag /usr/share/doc/qt4-doc-html/html/ 

Install Graphviz which creates the uml-like class diagramm.
Download at http://www.graphviz.org/Download.php


